  "raw_content": "Multi Head Attention 理论性能计算\n1、 MHA实现的功能：\n2、理论性能计算：\n3、 实际测量的性能\n4、当前supa实现\n5、优化策略\n6. 分段实测数据优化记录 ：\n7. pfc ：波形分析\n8 性能优化记录：\n\n优化点总结：\nmma-softmax-mma 串行执行，pipeline前后两个batch来overlap tcore and eu\n第三个mma用eu实现来减少softmax的stm和ldmma\nTLR够用的情况下，优化softmax部分的代码：如tcore→vector使用pingpong TLR, warp_max()使用pipeline实现来remove nop\n1、 MHA实现的功能：\nimage2023-12-13_15-49-16.png\n\nMultiHeadAttention包含了如上图中红框内的操作，主要是2个matmul和1个softmax。下面以decoder阶段为例，介绍MHA的功能。\n在decoder阶段，H=1，K V 矩阵用的是Kcache Vcache, 其shape为[N*head, seq_id, 128], 其中seq_id表示当前推断的第几个tocken。计算过程如下：\n第一个mma:\nin:  Q: [N*head, 1, 128]\nin:  Kcache:  [N*head, seq_id, 128]\nout:  score = Q*KcacheT = [N*head, 1, seq_id]\n\nsoftmax:\nin: score [N*head, 1, seq_id]\nout: score_ [N*head, 1, seq_id]\nsoftmax公式：\nimage2023-12-13_19-48-43.png\n\n\n第二个mma:\nin:  score_:  [N*head, 1, seq_id]\nin:  Vcache:  [N*head, seq_id, 128]\nout:  attn = score_*Vcache = [N*head, 1, 128]\n2、理论性能计算：\n\n\n多spc 拆分逻辑： 将N*head 维度 分到多个spc 计算\n下边按照上述mha的三个部分分别计算每部分cycle；（下面的N*head为每个spc 计算量）\nmma1:\n 左矩阵:  Q[N*head, 1, 128]    NUMA form HBM\n 右矩阵:  Kcache[N*head, seq_id, 128]   NUMA from hbm\n AB buf均从HBM load， 带宽按  38byte/cycle/spc\n load a cycle = N*head*64*128*sizeof(FP32)/38 → N*head*4*128*sizeof(FP32)/38\n load b cycle = N*head*(seq+63)/64*64*128*sizeof(FP32)/38 → N*head*(seq+3)/4*4*128*sizeof(FP32)/38 bank conflict?  19?\n mma1 cycle =  N*head*64*128* (seq+63)/64*64/8192\nmma的结果直接输出到TLR中\n该op计算为memory bound， 取load b cycle为该mma1的cycle\nsoftmax：\nin: score [N*head, 1, seq_id]     tlr\nout: score_ [N*head, 1, seq_id]\n根据softmax的公式：\nimage2023-12-13_19-50-24.png\n\nsoftmax分为2步计算：\n第一步：需要计算出每一行的max 以及expsum. mma1的结果保存在了TLR,可以直接用其计算max expsum，但通常decoder计算的seq较长，无法全部保存在TLR中，需要将其保存出去一次，\n第二步：等计算得到该行的max expsum, 会重新load到TLR,计算得到softmax结果，之后将保存到U#中。\nscore load一次， 保存2次， 该计算中认为都是从GMB load/store, 带宽按  256 byte/cycle/spc\nld_st_cycle = N*head*16* (seq+63)/64*64 *sizeof(FP32) *3 / 256,   按16行每个eu处理1行对齐，seq对齐到64\n计算cycle: 对于输入 [N*heads, 1,  seq],  对每一行需要的TLR,   (seq+31)/32,  求max expsum 需要2条 exp2  + 8条 乘加等指令，TLR内32thread间通过shuffle求max expsum需要10条shuffle+15条乘加+1条exp2,  得到max expsun后计算最终结果，每个TLR需要1条exp2+3条乘加， exp2 shuffle 按15cycle计算,每一行需要的计算cycle =   (seq+31)/32 * (3*15+11*2) + 11*15+15*2\n calc_cycle = N*head*( (seq+31)/32 *67 + 195)\n 计算可得calc_cycle 比 ld_st_cycle 要长， 取calc_cycle 为softmax的cycle数\nmma2:\n 左矩阵:  score_ [N*head, 1, seq_id]   NUMA form GMB\n 右矩阵:  Vcache[N*head, seq_id, 128]   NUMA form HBM\n out:  attn = score_*Vcache = [N*head, 1, 128]\n B buf从HBM load， 带宽按 每个spc  38byte/cycle\n load a cycle = N*head*4*(seq+127)/128*128*sizeof(FP32)/256   seq对齐到128\n load b cycle = N*head*(seq+127)/128*128*128*sizeof(FP32)/38   seq对齐到128 → N*head*(seq+3)/4*4*128*sizeof(FP32)/38\n mma cycle =  N*head*64*128* (seq+63)/64*64/8192\n 该op计算为memory bound， 取load b cycle为该mma2的cycle\n\n综上： 总cycle:  mma1_load_b + softmax + mma2_load_b\n理论性能计算结果：\n\n\nexpect理论值\n\nbatch\n\nheads\n\nseq\n\n总cycle(ms)\n\nmma1(ms)\n\nmma2(ms)\n\nsoftmax(ms)\n\nmma理论占比\n\nmma2理论占比\n\nsoftmax占比\n\ndecoder\n\n1\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.030257918\n\n0.0137971\n\n0.013797053\n\n0.00266381\n\n45.60%\n\n45.60%\n\n8.80%\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.035699813\n\n0.0155217\n\n0.017246316\n\n0.00293181\n\n43.48%\n\n48.31%\n\n8.21%\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.037692444\n\n0.0172463\n\n0.017246316\n\n0.00319981\n\n45.76%\n\n45.76%\n\n8.49%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.242063342\n\n0.1103764\n\n0.110376421\n\n0.0213105\n\n45.60%\n\n45.60%\n\n8.80%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.2855985\n\n0.1241735\n\n0.137970526\n\n0.0234545\n\n43.48%\n\n48.31%\n\n8.21%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.301539553\n\n0.1379705\n\n0.137970526\n\n0.0255985\n\n45.76%\n\n45.76%\n\n8.49%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.484126684\n\n0.2207528\n\n0.220752842\n\n0.042621\n\n45.60%\n\n45.60%\n\n8.80%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.571197\n\n0.2483469\n\n0.275941053\n\n0.046909\n\n43.48%\n\n48.31%\n\n8.21%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.603079105\n\n0.2759411\n\n0.275941053\n\n0.051197\n\n45.76%\n\n45.76%\n\n8.49%\n\n若mma可以将softmax的cycle完全掩盖，MHA可以达到的最好的理论值\n\n\n最好理论值\n\nbatch\n\nheads\n\nseq\n\n总cycle(ms)\n\nmma1(ms)\n\nmma2(ms)\n\ndecoder\n\n1\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.027594\n\n0.013797\n\n0.013797\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.032768\n\n0.015522\n\n0.017246\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.034493\n\n0.017246\n\n0.017246\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.220753\n\n0.110376\n\n0.110376\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.262144\n\n0.124173\n\n0.137971\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.275941\n\n0.137971\n\n0.137971\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.441506\n\n0.220753\n\n0.220753\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n576\n\n0.524288\n\n0.248347\n\n0.275941\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.551882\n\n0.275941\n\n0.275941\n3、 实际测量的性能\n\n测试方法： PFC得到的文件中统计 ctc_cycles(avg)  根据晓阳老师提示，这里采用cbi_cycles(max) 作为统计数据\n实测得到的数据如下：\n\n\n\n\nbatch\n\nheads\n\nseq\n\ntotal\n\nmma1\n\nmma2\n\nsoftmax\n\nmma占比\n\nmma2占比\n\nsoftmax占比\n\ndecoder\n\n1\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.055762\n\n0.014014\n\n0.017736\n\n0.014345\n\n25.13%\n\n31.81%\n\n25.73%\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.062225\n\n0.015104\n\n0.020865\n\n0.015085\n\n24.27%\n\n33.53%\n\n24.24%\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n768\n\n0.064725\n\n0.016028\n\n0.020665\n\n0.015826\n\n24.76%\n\n31.93%\n\n24.45%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.321562\n\n0.12386\n\n0.148665\n\n0.072571\n\n38.52%\n\n46.23%\n\n22.57%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.383092\n\n0.136177\n\n0.181835\n\n0.080097\n\n35.55%\n\n47.47%\n\n20.91%\n\n\n\n8\n\n32\n\n768\n\n0.382192\n\n0.14725\n\n0.18613\n\n0.087054\n\n38.53%\n\n48.70%\n\n22.78%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.599339\n\n0.221561\n\n0.278506\n\n0.140417\n\n36.97%\n\n46.47%\n\n23.43%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n640\n\n0.707671\n\n0.2627\n\n0.352909\n\n0.152174\n\n37.12%\n\n49.87%\n\n21.50%\n\n\n\n16\n\n32\n\n768\n\n0.750511\n\n0.293227\n\n0.362045\n\n0.165185\n\n39.07%\n\n48.24%\n\n22.01%\n采用cbi_cycles(max) 的数据：\n\n\n\n\nbatch\n\nheads\n\nseq\n\ntotal\n\nmma1\n\nmma2\n\nsoftmax\n\nmma占比\n\nmma2占比\n\nsoftmax占比\n\ndecoder\n\n1\n\n32\n\n512\n\n0.062207\n\n0.022225\n\n0.024016\n\n0.021242\n\n35.73%\n\n38.61%\n\n34.15%\n\n\n\n1\n\n32\n\n